\"has expanded by 11.4 percent since the end of 2019 and in its latest forecast, the IMF predicted U.S. growth</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455167761/image_1455167761.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741943-the-us-is-a-booming-economy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 08:26:39"}, {"id": "4741949", "title": "Columbia Capital Allocation Portfolios Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Asset Allocation Stocks Bonds Real estate Commodities are shown on the photo using the text\" data-id=\"1389343192\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Market overview</h2> <p>Global equity and bond markets generated attractive returns in the third quarter of 2024. Measuring the U.S. equity market, the S&amp;P 500 Index (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a>) rallied 5.89%, and the Russell 3000 Index rose 6.23%. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389343192/image_1389343192.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741949-columbia-capital-allocation-portfolios-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 08:25:00"}, {"id": "4741942", "title": "VT: Do You Think The U.S. Market Is Expensive - Check Out This ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A world globe marked with several national flag pins\" data-id=\"1303046106\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5220px\" height=\"3480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I recommend buying the Vanguard Total World Stock Index Fund ETF Shares (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VT\" title=\"Vanguard Total World Stock Index Fund ETF Shares\">VT</a></span>). The ETF offers good diversification in geographies that show good returns in periods of interest rate cuts in the United States.</p> <p>In addition, we</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741942-vt-do-you-think-the-us-market-is-expensive-check-out-this-etf", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 08:20:55"}, {"id": "4741938", "title": "Energy Transfer: Strong Fundamentals But Approaching Fair Value", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173614785/image_173614785.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oilfield # 14\" data-id=\"173614785\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3504px\" height=\"2336px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173614785/image_173614785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173614785/image_173614785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173614785/image_173614785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173614785/image_173614785.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/ge