lpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pump, oil industry equipment\" data-id=\"1327982065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">bjdlzx</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Back when John Goff (Chairman) and KKR first talked about forming Crescent Energy (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRGY\" title=\"Crescent Energy Company\">CRGY</a></span>) they both mentioned their success in building and selling companies. Crescent Energy is just one of many \"irons in the fire\" for both well-known investment entities. But</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327982065/image_1327982065.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalph