 deserve a closer look. I have already written about</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445251323/image_1445251323.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741931-semiconductor-stock-worth-watching-why-qualcomm-might-be-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 07:01:34"}, {"id": "4741930", "title": "8x8: Further Upside Hinges On A Return To Sustained Organic Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"close up soft focus on telephone devices at office desk for customer service support concept\" data-id=\"992782254\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/992782254/image_992782254.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Chainarong Prasertthai/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div c